# UI Rules

## Design System

- shadcn/ui primitives in `components/ui/` — extend, don't fork.
- Use CVA for component variants (see `button.tsx`).
- Semantic color tokens from CSS variables — no hardcoded hex in features.

## Components

- Presentational components: no data fetching.
- Container/feature components: hooks + data, pass props down.
- Reusable patterns: `DataTable`, `PageHeader`, `EmptyState`, `ErrorState`, `LoadingSkeleton`.

## Forms

- React Hook Form + Zod resolver (when added) — schemas from `@uk-phv/validation`.
- Show inline field errors from API `details[]`.

## Dispatch UI

- Live board: booking status chips, driver assignment modal, compliance warnings.
- Color-blind safe status indicators (icon + text, not color alone).

## Responsive

- Breakpoints: mobile dispatch read-only summary, full board at `lg+`.
